Maxima, in her funky animal/jet mode detected the pods. 'Charming,' she 
thought.

"Thrust! Retrieve the 2 new bots at the nearby crash site. Coordinates are 
Tango-Delta-Bravo-46-13 ... just slightly to the NE of us a couple kilometers. 
Retrieve them then rendezvous with us at the Ark location. I'm sure we will 
need them for the battle defense." 

She flew on quickly towards the Ark.
